Elephant

The king of the jungle

<>Elephant (Loxodonta africana): The African elephant is the largest land animal on Earth, known for its intelligence, strong social bonds, and incredible memory. They can be seen roaming the savannahs and forests, using their trunks for everything from feeding to communication.
